sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin
    participant AdminPanel
    participant Backend
    participant Database

    %% Admin View Orders
    Note over Admin,Database: Admin - View All Orders Flow
    Admin->>AdminPanel: Navigate to Orders page
    AdminPanel->>Backend: GET /api/order/list
    Backend->>Database: Fetch all orders
    Database-->>Backend: All orders array
    Backend-->>AdminPanel: Return orders
    AdminPanel-->>Admin: Display orders with details

    %% Admin Update Order Status
    Note over Admin,Database: Admin - Update Order Status Flow
    Admin->>AdminPanel: Change order status dropdown
    AdminPanel->>Backend: POST /api/order/status {orderId, status}
    Backend->>Database: Find and update order status
    Database-->>Backend: Order updated
    Backend-->>AdminPanel: Success response
    AdminPanel->>Backend: GET /api/order/list (refresh)
    Backend->>Database: Fetch updated orders
    Database-->>Backend: Updated orders array
    Backend-->>AdminPanel: Return updated orders
    AdminPanel-->>Admin: Display updated order list

    %% Admin Monitor Order Details
    Note over Admin,Database: Admin - Monitor Order Details Flow
    Admin->>AdminPanel: View order in list
    AdminPanel->>AdminPanel: Display order items
    AdminPanel->>AdminPanel: Display customer address
    AdminPanel->>AdminPanel: Display payment status
    AdminPanel->>AdminPanel: Display total amount
    AdminPanel-->>Admin: Show complete order information
